---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | ZynfexGame" description="Privacy Policy and terms for ZynfexGame.tech">
	<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-8 text-gray-300">
		<h1 class="text-4xl text-white font-black mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
		<p class="mb-4">Last updated: March 2026</p>
		
		<h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-bold mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
		<p class="mb-4">At ZynfexGame, accessible from zynfexgame.me, one of our main priorities is the privacy of our visitors. This Privacy Policy document contains types of information that is collected and recorded by ZynfexGame and how we use it.</p>
		
		<h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-bold mt-8 mb-4">2. Cookies and Web Beacons</h2>
		<p class="mb-4">Like any other website, ZynfexGame uses "cookies". These cookies are used to store information including visitors' preferences, and the pages on the website that the visitor accessed or visited. We use Google Analytics and Google AdSense to serve ads based on your prior visits.</p>
		
		<h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-bold mt-8 mb-4">3. Third Party Privacy Policies</h2>
		<p class="mb-4">ZynfexGame provides access to HTML5 games via third-party embedded iframes (e.g., GameDistribution). These third-party ad servers or ad networks uses technologies like cookies, JavaScript, or Web Beacons that are used in their respective advertisements and links that appear on ZynfexGame. We have no control over these third-party trackers.</p>

		<h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-bold mt-8 mb-4">4. Consent</h2>
		<p class="mb-4 pb-10">By using our website, you hereby consent to our Privacy Policy and agree to its Terms and Conditions.</p>
	</div>
</Layout>
